@startuml
title AI Request Pipeline
start
:Persist user message;
:Load bounded history and conversation memory;
:Interpret graduate query;
if (Ambiguous or unsupported?) then (yes)
  :Persist safe clarification;
  stop
endif
:Resolve follow-up and retrieve context;
:Apply context budget;
if (Request fits?) then (yes)
  :Call configured AI provider;
else (no)
  :Create safe budget fallback;
endif
:Extract citations and persist assistant message;
stop
@enduml
